---
title: Tex-Mex Chickpea Quesadillas with Cucumber Salsa & Cheddar Cheese
description: All hail the king of toasted breads, the cheesiest and most noble of dinner options, the mighty quesadilla! Tonight, we’ve filled
them with a delicious mix of nutritious ingredients and paired it with chickpeas, spring onion and cucumber salsa.

*We’ve replaced the black beans in this recipe with chickpeas due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
